    "form_header_text": "Fiscal Year 2027: Appropriations Request for Congressman Vicente Gonzalez - TX34",
    "form_instructions_text": "The deadline for Fiscal Year 2027 general requests is Friday, March 6, 2026, at 6 p.m. CT. The House Committee on Appropriations responsibilities cover all federal funding including transportation, housing, science, education, energy, labor, defense, environment, justice, homeland security, agriculture, health and human services. Members of the House have the opportunity to submit requests to the Appropriations Committee for consideration into the annual appropriations bills. I am proud to submit requests that support Texas's 34th Congressional District. If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to call the Washington, D.C. Office at (202) 225-2531 or email at TX34DCOffice@mail.house.gov.",
